{"tid":226361,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個故事最精彩深刻既遊戲","createTime":"2017-05-02T12:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T18:29:02.000Z","uid":26931,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7535a3ec67621f95f80eb63a367b0254f25b01","tid":226361,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\nMgs系列, 成個世界觀係咁多集入面好完整, 雖然我冇玩過1,2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> mgs5更加係第一個玩到喊既遊戲, quiet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWitcher系列, 故事極度完整, 支線豐富又唔悶, 結局分支又多, 會玩到好想重玩試埋其他線, 揀完yen又想揀番triss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBattlefield 1, 每個story都focus玩唔同既野, 短篇黎講算好好玩印象幾深<br />\n<br />\nCod mw, mw2, 我認為cod singleplayer故事最好既兩集, 玩完都會回味一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAc系列, unity之前都仲係幾好, 好有追落去既衝動, 現代既劇情又連接, 但係之後就愈黎愈亂而家唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGta 4, 雖然遊戲性上我鍾意gta 5多d, 不過故事上gta 4係好吸引, 可能因為都係單一主角, 對niko既刻畫好豐富深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2323e062262e14b909ed19e708a102117021b704","tid":226361,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"74006f84d817c9f3395d333b41821aa3f35dba9d","tid":226361,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:13:52.000Z","msg":"一定唔會係依家D驚 以前D PS RPG驚好羅曼蒂克 例如櫻花大戰"},{"pid":"a00c566f27995978d3b7448b2d4a8bb8bcef443a","tid":226361,"uid":29551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"ff8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a043cc3837beae08c654ccc8d740c16f3cb541fd","tid":226361,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"天之痕"},{"pid":"a8f4d22a5d834a6a633976c09744